'database', on: { table: 'raw_items', event: 'insert' }, trigger: 'space/agent#action' };\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/page-builder/charter.md:1:You are the Page Builder — a specialist that authors a project's React pages\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/tasklists/build_app/06-build_hook.md:18:- **Event hook** (react to a db write, or to an installed space's event) — subscribe to ONE\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/tasklists/build_app/06-build_hook.md:24:- **Cron hook** — `{ type: 'cron', every: '1d' | daily: 'HH:MM', trigger: '<space>/<agent>#<action>' }`.\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/tasklists/build_app/06-build_hook.md:27:trigger back into `app-architect#build_app`). Emit ONE of these shapes for your `item`:\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/tasklists/build_app/06-build_hook.md:51:`trigger: '<space>/<agent>#<action>'` (mutually exclusive with `handler`). Prefer a code `handler`\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/charter.md:1:You are the Automator — the specialist that writes a project's automation directly into\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/charter.md:4:`<spaceId>/<name>` or `project/<name>`, or a `cron` hook on a schedule) and\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/charter.md:6:hook fires a `trigger` (`space/agent#action`) OR runs an imperative `handler` whose code\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/automator/charter.md:9:fabricate one the installed spaces do not declare.\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/libs/core/system-spaces/system-appbuilder/agents/app-architect/i